Pre-Game Insights: USA vs Nepal cricket series, the Stake Stars and Summits Trophy, is planned to begin on October 17, 2024, with three T20Is between Team USA and Team Nepal at the Grand Prairie Cricket Stadium in Grand Prairie, Texas.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Stake will host fan interaction activities and giveaways throughout the season.

The Stake Stars and Summits Trophy will be followed by the Cricket World Cup League 2 series, which will include USA Cricket, Nepal Cricket, and the Scotland Cricket Team competing in six ODIs for points towards qualification to the next ICC ODI World Cup.
Others: USA Cricket, the governing body of cricket in the United States, has announced a sponsorship deal with Stake, a leading online casino platform.
The partnership will allow Stake to engage with both new and experienced cricket fans, while also helping to expand the sport in America.
